Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.70,0:29:15.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After the destruction of the family,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.33,0:29:19.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Inumaru sets out on a journey in search of Maroko,\Nvisiting street-side soba vendors everywhere,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.46,0:29:22.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,remembering the day when the Canadian\Ngoldenrod blossomed brightly,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.46,0:29:25.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,remembering the day when the yellow airship arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.51,0:29:28.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time on the last episode of Gosenzosama Banbanzai:
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.09,0:29:30.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Papillon Dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.60,0:29:32.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You won't be disappointed!
